{"tid":1327827,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［記你老母］商業電台記者被警員阻撓採訪兼被警棍打【附警員阻撓片段】","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T17:59:52.000Z","uid":204194,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4f4f3a8fcfb28c4fcf29c8486172ce4bdbd92a","tid":1327827,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:45:45.000Z","msg":"【兩度阻採訪】本台記者兩次警民衝突期間，都被警方阻撓採訪。兩次當時的情況如何？記者陳皓為自白，並附當時片段。<br />\n<br />\n個人簡單概括：<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">金鐘</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 6月12號，記者陳皓為身穿反光衣並多次表明自己為記者，卻被速龍小隊推撞，更被警棍打中右手手臂，兼被「記你老母」。<br />\n<br />\n2. 記者即場向現場警方傳媒聯絡隊投訴，但當時(6月12號)不能做紀錄或備案，除非馬上到警署，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>現場警方傳媒聯絡隊亦指出，何時作出投訴，並不會影響記者追究的權利。</strong></span> (有錄音)<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沙田</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n3. 7月14號，沙田新城市廣場巴士總站對出單車徑，在拍攝期間，被警員用胡椒噴劑噴臉，並在盾牌推撞下趕離現場。<br />\n<br />\n4. 喝令記者不準用毛巾抹走臉上的胡椒噴劑，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「就係你哋啲記者，搞亂個社會」</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 因得知記者身份，被各種針對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LE9XtsM2hyU&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLE9XtsM2hyU%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=058b7b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LE9XtsM2hyU&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"1bb8239d88373145d4b21d613b522467e0dcb5d9","tid":1327827,"uid":204194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:47:59.000Z","msg":"聲援記者，文宣做野。"},{"pid":"99859632852509dff3c1bde8b7db7328f889e60e","tid":1327827,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"84d186a5c0a6523f74dbb2cb3e91dbbaeb2404aa","tid":1327827,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:53:48.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"d6a72823582aea1b6e2b3ddb969